snippet.title: Fisher Haven - Trailer
snippet.description:
An immersive fishing adventure where you compete in the island's annual competition. Upgrade your gear, discover unique baits, and form alliances with fellow fishers to maximize your chances of victory. Explore diverse zones, catch over 100 fish types, and hunt down 7 rare species.

Fisher Haven releases 10th of april 2025: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3593860/Fisher_Haven/
